<h1>Renderer cleanup test (Issue #3209)</h1>

<p>
  Mounts a renderer function that returns a teardown closure. Once Issue #3209 is
  implemented, navigating away via Turbo should cause the framework to invoke the
  teardown — unmounting the React root and firing the tree's <code>useEffect</code>
  cleanup, which sets <code>window.__rendererCleanupRan__ = true</code>.
</p>

<%= react_component(
  "RendererCleanupTest",
  props: {},
  prerender: false,
  id: "RendererCleanupTest-1",
  auto_load_bundle: false,
) %>

<p>
  <%= link_to "Navigate away (Turbo)", manual_render_test_path, id: "renderer-cleanup-leave-link" %>
</p>
